content.item: 1.新增第三方服务功能“转账自动回复”，用户可为有价值的信息设置付费YOYO，需要的用户可付费YOYO获取信息.
2.UI界面全面升级，优化了大量用户交互体验.

1.Newly added 3rd party service feature --- “Auto-reply for transfers”；users can set the amount YOYO they would like to charge for their valuable information, and other users in need can pay that amount YOYO to receive that information.
2.Fully Upgraded UI, optimized a large portion of user interaction experience.
